&lt;p&gt;HMP &amp; YOI Hindley&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These positions are for registered general health nurses, or student nurses in training who wish to work in prison nursing from qualifying under preceptorship.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time position, however depending on requests we may be able to accommodate flexible or family friendly hours. The hours are over a 7 day period, and include early shifts, late shifts and nights.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting and rewarding position for a motivated individual with high standards of clinical care, we will be happy to support any training needs that are required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
